The temperature was well below freezing, but covered in 5mm rubber wetsuits with 7mm booties & gloves, @luanasilva__ @beccaspeak were actually surprisingly warm in this chilly late winter session in the North Atlantic. A day where most surfers would have stayed home with the heater on, these gals were more than stoked to get in the water before sunrise. It’s been a pleasure over the years to witness more and more gals get excited to surf, go on expeditions and fill the lineups of cold water waves. 

